headline: Garmin (GRMN): Assessing Valuation as Shares Continue Steady Climb

headline: Garmin named Most Innovative Marine Company for 2025
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) is proud to announce it has been named the top company in the 2025 EPIC Awards for the third consecutive year by Soundings Trade Only, a leading trade publication for the recreational boating industry.
